<div id="index-banner" class="parallax-container">
	<div class="section no-pad-bot">
		<div class="container">
			<br><br>
			<h1 class="header center">Krewe</h1>
			<div class="row center">
				<h5 class="header col s12 light">The best way to form your social network</h5>
			</div>
			<div class="row center">
				<% if current_user %>
					<%= link_to "Home", user_path(current_user), class: "modal-trigger", class: 'btn-large waves-effect blue' %>
				<% else %>
					<%= link_to "Sign Up", new_user_path, class: "modal-trigger",  class: 'btn-large waves-effect blue', remote: true %>
				<% end %>
			</div>
			<br><br>

		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="parallax"><%= video_tag 'diner.mp4', autoplay: true, loop: true %></div>
</div>


<div class="container">
	<div class="section">

		<!--   Icon Section   -->
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col s12 m4">
				<div class="icon-block">
					<h2 class="center brown-text"><i class="material-icons">group</i></h2>
					<h5 class="center">Krewe connects you with a group of people</h5>

					<p class="light">No more profiles to browse through and superficial judgements. No swiping like you're everyday dating app. You just start off with a group of at most six people. We want you to feel as comfortable as possible and we belive that being in a small group will make that possible. </p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="col s12 m4">
				<div class="icon-block">
					<h2 class="center brown-text"><i class="material-icons">my_location</i></h2>
					<h5 class="center">Everyone lives in your neighborhood</h5>

					<p class="light">We get that you're busy. Therefore, we only connect you with people who live close by so that going to hang out with them is not a big ordeal. With Krewe, getting together after a busy work day at a local bar or coffee shop is easy as everyone is within walking distance.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="col s12 m4">
				<div class="icon-block">
					<h2 class="center brown-text"><i class="material-icons">insert_invitation</i></h2>
					<h5 class="center">Meeting up is easy</h5>

					<p class="light">We provide you the tools to make it really easy to set up things to do and get everyone involved. Doing thing over and over again with your group is simple and fun, helping your form strong bonds and connections.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

	</div>
</div>


